name: Flagship (V)
Lore: 'After the Battle of Yavin, it was politically necessary to demonstrate the unstoppable might of the Empire. The Executor and Death Squadron ensured this objective.',
Text: 'Deploy on your Star Destroyer.  It draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise (two if Executor).  Counter Assault is canceled.  During your move phase, Landing Claw is canceled here.  Once per turn, may take an admiral or Executor site into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.(Errata Text - September 9th, 2009)',
